item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_LoginFailed
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_LoginFailed Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_LOGIN_FAILED data type contains information for specific responses from the getPortalLogin API. This class is indicative of a request where there was an inability to login based on the information that was provided. Local accounts The list of linked accounts for the authenticated SoftLayer customer portal user. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Account[] errorMessage Type: string statusKeyName Type: string
